          <span class="accordion-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-body" id="acc-body-4" role="region" aria-labelledby="acc-btn-4">
          <div class="accordion-content">
            Monthly subscription fees are only part of the cost. Each installed application loads <strong>additional scripts</strong> on your storefront, increasing page load time and reducing Core Web Vitals scores — directly impacting SEO ranking and conversion rates.
            <br /><br />
            Large app stacks also create <strong>operational complexity</strong>: overlapping functionality, data synchronisation failures, and integration fragility. For high-growth brands, these hidden costs often exceed the original subscription fees.
            <br /><br />
            Tracking apps like <a href="/elevar-alternative">Elevar ($150+/mo)</a> and <a href="/triple-whale-alternative">Triple Whale ($299+/mo)</a> can be fully replaced by <a href="/capi-shield">CAPI Shield</a> — a free server-side tracking setup achieving identical EMQ scores at $0/month.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item" id="acc-5">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" id="acc-btn-5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="acc-body-5">
          <h2>Understanding Your Shopify Efficiency Score</h2>
          <span class="accordion-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-body" id="acc-body-5" role="region" aria-labelledby="acc-btn-5">
          <div class="accordion-content">
            Your <strong>automation efficiency score</strong> runs from 0 to 100 and measures how optimised your stack is relative to what's achievable with free automation:
            <ul>
              <li><strong>80–100:</strong> Excellent — lean stack, minimal unnecessary overhead</li>
              <li><strong>60–79:</strong> Good — some apps replaceable, moderate savings available</li>
              <li><strong>40–59:</strong> Moderate — significant savings, multiple apps to review</li>
              <li><strong>0–39:</strong> High overhead — major savings available via free automation</li>
            </ul>
            The score reflects <strong>operational infrastructure efficiency</strong>, not store revenue. Use the <a href="/shopify-app-stack-kill-or-keep-auditor">Kill-or-Keep Auditor</a> for a deeper verdict on each individual app in your stack.
          </div>
